_auto:good%2Cw_380/MjE0NDEzMDg1MTU3MzY4ODU1/meghan-markle-ralph-lauren.jpg 380w, https://fashionista.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cfl_progressive%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_620/MjE0NDEzMDg1MTU3MzY4ODU1/meghan-markle-ralph-lauren.jpg 620w, https://fashionista.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cfl_progressive%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_700/MjE0NDEzMDg1MTU3MzY4ODU1/meghan-markle-ralph-lauren.jpg 700w\"/\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"meghan-markle-ralph-lauren\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://fashionista.com/.image/t_share/MjE0NDEzMDg1MTU3MzY4ODU1/meghan-markle-ralph-lauren.jpg\" data-src=\"https://fashionista.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cfl_progressive%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_700/MjE0NDEzMDg1MTU3MzY4ODU1/meghan-markle-ralph-lauren.jpg\" height=\"4988\" width=\"3163\" srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7\" itemprop=\"contentUrl url\"/\u003e\u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/phoenix-picture\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003e\u003cp itemprop=\"author\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003ePhoto: Craig Barritt/Getty Images for TIME\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cem\u003eEver since\u003c/em\u003e\u003cem\u003e \u003ca href=\"https://fashionista.com/2017/11/meghan-markle-prince-harry-engagement-ring-coat\"\u003eannouncing her engagement to Prince Harry\u003c/a\u003e,\u003c/em\u003e\u003cem\u003e the world\u0026#39;s eyes have been fixed on \u003ca href=\"https://fashionista.com/tag/meghan-markle\"\u003eMeghan Markle\u003c/a\u003e — and her style. We\u0026#39;ll be following the \u003c/em\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://fashionista.com/2017/12/meghan-markle-effect-fashion-brands\"\u003e\u003cem\u003eMeghan Markle Effect\u003c/em\u003e™\u003c/a\u003e \u003cem\u003ewith our column, \u0026#34;\u003ca href=\"https://fashionista.com/tag/meghan-markle-wore-a-thing\"\u003eMeghan Markle Wore a Thing\u003c/a\u003e.\u0026#34;\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eWearing suits in spring weather can be tricky, mainly because most of them are too heavy to be worn in warmer weather. For Meghan Markle, however, no season can best her chic workwear.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eOn Wednesday, the Duchess of Sussex spoke at the Time100 Summit at New York City\u0026#39;s Lincoln Center, wearing a tan linen \u003ca href=\"https://fashionista.com/designers/ralph-lauren\"\u003eRalph Lauren\u003c/a\u003e suit paired with a crisp white button-down. The quiet \u003ca href=\"https://fashionista.com/tag/luxury\"\u003eluxury\u003c/a\u003e-coded outfit consists of the brand\u0026#39;s relaxed-fit \u003ca href=\"https://rstyle.me/+niA1PtLxp4CF_m4FeEqqvQ\" rel=\"noopener\" onclick=\"return phoenixTrackClickEvent(this, event);\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eRussell Twill Blazer\u003c/a\u003e featuring subtle power shoulders. Waist down, rather than lean into her penchant for skinny \u003ca href=\"https://fashionista.com/tag/jeans\"\u003ejeans\u003c/a\u003e, Markle switched it up by going for matching wide-leg, \u003ca href=\"https://rstyle.me/+teScEVPHOqoyVuxgq6WFUQ\" rel=\"noopener\" onclick=\"return phoenixTrackClickEvent(this, event);\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eTwill Pleated\u003c/a\u003e trousers. \u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cfigure itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/ImageObject\"\u003e\u003cphoenix-picture\u003e\u003ca\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource type=\"image/webp\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1240px) 700px, (min-width: 675px) 620px, calc(100vw - 40px)\" data-srcset=\"https://fashionista.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_380/MjE0NDEzMTM5NjQ5NzY3MjA0/meghan-markle.webp 380w, https://fashionista.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_620/MjE0NDEzMTM5NjQ5NzY3MjA0/meghan-markle.webp 620w, https://fashionista.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_700/MjE0NDEzMTM5NjQ5NzY3MjA0/meghan-markle.webp 700w\"/\u003e\u003csource sizes=\"(min-width: 1240px) 700px, (min-width: 675px) 620px, calc(100vw - 40px)\" data-srcset=\"https://fashionista.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_